{"tid":230240,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"公司個新同事竟然唔跟埋我地去捐血","createTime":"2017-05-05T08:10:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T03:02:20.000Z","uid":36497,"like":8,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3dbf8b5855190df04682aa4265b540221a08fe22","tid":230240,"uid":36497,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:10:57.000Z","msg":"個個都知近日血庫唔夠血<br />\n咁公司就建議大家去捐血 所以三點就放左大家走<br />\n咁我地一班同事就約埋一齊去大家樂食個tea<br />\n之後再去荃灣捐血<br />\n<br />\n咁我就叫埋個新同事去捐血啦<br />\n點知佢話佢未捐過 又話唔知d血比邊個用 所以唔捐<br />\n平時又要串柒柒咁 唔埋我地堆<br />\n<br />\n於是我忍唔住講句 比你老母用架<br />\n你唔撚捐啦嘛 咁你留係公司做野<br />\n<br />\n結果我地成班同事去捐血 佢就留底做我地d野<br />\n<br />\n下星期返到黎 一定玩死佢<br />\n咁無愛心呀啦 唔肯幫人呀拿 抵你比我地恰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24648931cef955b1d231d6fa8732e42e0655aaef","tid":230240,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"依家啲90後係咁 冇家教！"},{"pid":"995f0b06c77e4ff56c1e8ee3ecb3f60b984874bc","tid":230240,"uid":27731,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:14:49.000Z","msg":"我估個新同事一定係90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁冇同情心"},{"pid":"78513125a0fc9feae79b53a9f0f278cc0a6fc7d5","tid":230240,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"上次個90後竟然問可唔可以淨捐100ml <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講出黎都冇面啦 我地個個老鬼都捐開30 磅"},{"pid":"8ea8a49ed8200e115db4f2108f3774db838c4858","tid":230240,"uid":101282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"無提到90後，0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e4c0f2f631a5926d0980a22c0f644bedb39c10e","tid":230240,"uid":49993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"唉屌，唔捐血都比人屌，又話早收工，依家仲叫我做撚哂公司所有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得翻我一個係公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a15158eadc4c1c28c3fe25b4cd2fa463330831","tid":230240,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"個新同事係咪90後？"},{"pid":"4f06003a5fd20625e33480fadf8b4c533ca1e305","tid":230240,"uid":13067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:28:11.000Z","msg":"垃圾90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b8b8869b8dffe1746ce72c65e9c4bbc2e59b65","tid":230240,"uid":61586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:29:09.000Z","msg":"支持90後系列"},{"pid":"5598a456a8f1f385bc301ec8c154ccd23f42a558","tid":230240,"uid":80593,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:29:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依家啲90後係咁 冇家教！</blockquote><br />\n捐唔捐血，好個人意願。咁都叫無家教？咁你唔去捐錢，唔捐器官？<br />\n講無家教前，用下你個豬腦諗下野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPS唔係個個人都可以捐血，貧血，地中海貧血，血小板少...........性取向，疾病。"},{"pid":"bdc98f106688ea2db7e1d49b8e421c52e494e9be","tid":230240,"uid":38688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:30:14.000Z","msg":"唔係話針對d 90後"},{"pid":"dffc6f5dc28ea34566128a8dcabe5967d8aec872","tid":230240,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:34:16.000Z","msg":"吾系話針對d 90後<br />\n但系近期話吾捐血個d多數都系90後"},{"pid":"d1d4f07dea2c04c0dac4661220b2d478510e24a0","tid":230240,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無提到90後，0分重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重你老母